**Supported Chains:**
- **Ethereum (ETH)**: Bridge ETH, USDC, USDT, wrapped tokens
- **Binance Smart Chain (BSC)**: Bridge BNB, BUSD, wrapped tokens
- **Polygon (MATIC)**: Bridge MATIC, USDC, wrapped tokens

**Technical Details:**
- **Guardian Network**: 19 independent validators (includes Coinbase, Jump, etc.)
- **Consensus**: 2/3+ guardians must agree (13+ signatures)
- **VAA**: Verifiable Action Approval = cryptographic proof of lock
- **Atomic Swap**: Either completes fully or reverts completely
- **No Custodian**: Fully decentralized bridge (no central authority)

**Security Guarantees:**
- **Multi-Signature**: Requires 13+ independent validators
- **Time Lock**: 15-second finality on Ethereum â†’ Immediate on Solana
- **Slashing**: Guardians stake collateral, lose funds for bad behavior
- **Audit Trail**: All bridges publicly verifiable on-chain

**Fee Structure:**
- **Wormhole Fee**: ~$1 (paid to guardians)
- **Source Chain Gas**: Varies by network (ETH high, BSC/Polygon low)
- **Solana Gas**: < $0.001 (negligible)
- **PV3 Fee**: 0% bridge fee (we want users to deposit!)